Description:
------------
From the creators of the award-winning franchise, Just Dance, and the success Michael Jackson The Experience, comes the new ABBA You Can Dance.

With 25 songs that never go out of fashion, like "Dancing Queen," "Mamma Mia", "Fernando", "Waterloo" and "Take A Chance On Me," ABBA You Can Dance invites you to stomp the dance floor and relive the golden age of pop music with one of the biggest musical sensations of the world.

Dance with up to 4 players or sing the songs of ABBA You Can Dance will become an unforgettable fun time with your family or your friends, no matter what generation you belong.
